## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="1af04-102">安全关键操作是影响代码访问安全性，例如通过使用代码访问安全检查的禁止显示的特权提升的操作<xref:System.Security.CodeAccessPermission.Assert%2A>方法、 调用不安全的托管的代码和等。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1af04-102">Security-critical operations are actions that affect code access security, such as elevation of privilege through suppression of code access security checks by using the <xref:System.Security.CodeAccessPermission.Assert%2A> method, calling unsafe managed code, and so forth.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1af04-103">任一<xref:System.Security.SecurityCriticalAttribute>属性或<xref:System.Security.SecuritySafeCriticalAttribute>属性必须应用于代码的代码执行安全关键操作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1af04-103">Either the <xref:System.Security.SecurityCriticalAttribute> attribute or the <xref:System.Security.SecuritySafeCriticalAttribute> attribute must be applied to code for the code to perform security-critical operations.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="1af04-104"><xref:System.Security.SecurityCriticalAttribute>等效于完全信任的链接要求。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1af04-104">The <xref:System.Security.SecurityCriticalAttribute> is equivalent to a link demand for full trust.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1af04-105">类型或成员标记有<xref:System.Security.SecurityCriticalAttribute>只能由完全受信任的代码; 可以调用它没有到请求的特定权限。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1af04-105">A type or member marked with the <xref:System.Security.SecurityCriticalAttribute> can be called only by fully trusted code; it does not have to demand specific permissions.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1af04-106">它不能由部分受信任代码调用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1af04-106">It cannot be called by partially trusted code.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1af04-107">应用<xref:System.Security.SecurityCriticalAttribute>级别在程序集标识为安全关键的程序集的程序集。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1af04-107">Applying the <xref:System.Security.SecurityCriticalAttribute> at the assembly level identifies the assembly as a security-critical assembly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1af04-108">整个程序集可以通过来识别为关键设置作用域参数<xref:System.Security.SecurityCriticalScope.Everything?displayProperty=nameWithType>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1af04-108">The entire assembly can be identified as critical by setting the scope parameter <xref:System.Security.SecurityCriticalScope.Everything?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
